1. To properly run the code, first install anaconda (be sure to answer yes on add to path):

	Ubuntu: https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/linux/
	Windows: https://www.anaconda.com/products/individual#windows

2. Create an environment with the provided file (you may need to restart your shell first):

	conda env create -f environment.yml
	
3. Activate the new environment:

	conda activate pgmpy

4. Navigate to the directory with the code and run with "python pgm_tutorial.py"
